{"tid":25510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"必勝客速遞員炒車亡","createTime":"2016-12-06T07:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T09:38:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"746308b3aa5ac53c6ce054b2d4c8f3a5709828cf","tid":25510,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856426&d=DHJINZCkzmJxfC0bBCNoCksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=4965297a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20161206%2F19856426&h=ef8c92b0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20161206/19856426</a><br />\n<br />\n必勝客速遞員炒車亡<br />\n<br />\n14,699<br />\nInitial ImagePlay Button Image<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n<br />\n ■外賣電單車與拖車相撞損毀，速遞員傷重不治。張家豪攝<br />\n■外賣電單車與拖車相撞損毀，速遞員傷重不治。張家豪攝<br />\n【本報訊】葵涌發生奪命車禍，25歲Pizza Hut（必勝客）外賣速遞員，昨晚駕駛外賣電單車沿葵福路行駛，至近盛福街對開交界路口，與一輛拖車迎頭相撞，速遞員人仰車翻傷重不治。警方不排除拖車司機沒留意路面引致車禍，呼籲目擊者提供資料。<br />\n<br />\n遭拖車猛撞<br />\n事發昨晚近8時，喪命的25歲Pizza Hut外賣速遞員姓郭，當時駕駛外賣電單車，沿葵福路往葵芳方向行駛，當到達盛福街對開交界路口，此時一輛拖車沿葵福路往荃灣方向馳至，其間與電單車發生猛烈相撞，速遞員飛彈地上重傷，口鼻滲血。<br />\n警方趕至封鎖現場，救護員替事主急救後送院，其後證實死亡，醫生初步懷疑因內臟重創致死。速遞員家人趕抵醫院，驚聞噩耗傷心痛哭。而拖車司機則未有受傷，由警員帶上警車協助調查。警方調查期間，Pizza Hut亦派人到場善後。<br />\n事件中，Pizza Hut外賣電單車車頭嚴重損毀，碎片散滿一地，拖車鬼面罩亦甩脫。警方調查懷疑拖車當時在讓線，但未確定對面線沒有車輛便駛出釀成意外。<br />\n■記者張家豪  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n運輸工生日卡藏毒寄收押所　一度棄保潛逃判囚22月<br />\n下一則<br />\n兩夫婦為錢嘈交　妻燒炭變燒屋"},{"pid":"19c66aebbbdc0d7d3b5578e38119b596559794f8","tid":25510,"uid":12287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:17:57.000Z","msg":"rip...."},{"pid":"a8e1a9e99444def0d16331814341f70f7c45679d","tid":25510,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dd9f3b7e1142eed17395a87d9f4dc2f3442a25","tid":25510,"uid":56903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b19c250a67da6d4fa0b3bc045b9eb0f8e24b4af","tid":25510,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"咁咪成堆pizza撞到滿天飛？"},{"pid":"c3d57db35aec1ffa67d13b37db7205aee3ac3493","tid":25510,"uid":12614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"r i p<br />\n不過pizza仔成日搵命博"},{"pid":"5ec1560f2352a7cd05aba0ae6e8cea5626f8bc96","tid":25510,"uid":12675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:32:26.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"3abe59f9e6cce812d0e1a7c932ae9f352e7d60c3","tid":25510,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3828852b4b398b838c2e10e1d2e45d0eadf0ce","tid":25510,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:34:14.000Z","msg":"RIP <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵命博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78bafb8ed105a9df4f6d24d39dac1c7396908dfd","tid":25510,"uid":57411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:34:44.000Z","msg":"打份工,命都無埋,陰工..<br />\nR.I.P"},{"pid":"a7f3c1994888a908b3fa88a20afdbbbc3f2f4a09","tid":25510,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20161206/large/06la7p1new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20161206%2Flarge%2F06la7p1new.jpg&h=1701145c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6e78b6867ee109bcd45f7945adfb7c69409d05d","tid":25510,"uid":2060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:36:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98104cd9df6488af04f3114a9aa6458e671d6fa6","tid":25510,"uid":46644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27ffbadf8f4759c533b18d3fbc1d8a901d067484","tid":25510,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:38:45.000Z","msg":"最慘係呢D送PIZZA係簽左假自僱<br />\nPIZZA HUT可能一毫子都唔賠"},{"pid":"fbdbcda5e4d7516e76d71bb5890bf2f8f34e3bfd","tid":25510,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:40:26.000Z","msg":"工會表示，麥當勞將外賣服務外判給域迅快遞有限公司後，毫無監管，對車手的各項僱員應有保障漠不關心，即使域迅和車手簽署所謂的「承包協議」，麥當勞也視若無睹，變相縱容域迅公司以假自僱的方式剝削員工，導致員工無法得到《僱傭條例》、《僱員補償條例》和《強積金條例》等法例下的僱員保障。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告效應下，再加上麥當勞公司的20-40分鐘服務承諾，麥當勞車手不斷發生大大小小的工傷。嚴重的有2009年2月頭一名車手因交通車禍去世；也有員工因為車禍工傷需動大手術，休假數個月，但是毫無補償。<br />\n<br />\n工會又指出，員工在職期間，除了每天工作的時薪收入外，沒有任何的假期和福利，有員工向公司辭職，更被扣去7日的工資；也有員工送外賣發生交通意外，被公司扣薪以支付車輛的維修費用，可見域迅公司剝削員工<br />\n<br />\n工會表示，其他提供外賣服務已久的連鎖快餐集團，包括Pizza Hut和肯德基，都是直接聘請外賣車手，員工可以得到僱員的相關保障。工會批評麥當勞作為跨國連鎖集團的龍頭公司，卻行了一個極壞的先例，將外賣服務外判，剝削員工。"},{"pid":"d9dc18c672f9e3bce606c7ca147fcc7270740c61","tid":25510,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:45:06.000Z","msg":"啲pizza反而冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6028728bc3b4be0ed0c859169fc6d5bc472b40","tid":25510,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:46:27.000Z","msg":"25歲, 靠自己雙手賺錢<br />\n咁就死於非命, 真係好悲"},{"pid":"9d0a035703fc90e7a4716de6fbf4ac0e0410daeb","tid":25510,"uid":45644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T07:49:49.000Z","msg":"我都係25歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d948f6b35c9bfbd4814bab2a35859fd9bef0ea7e","tid":25510,"uid":833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip..."},{"pid":"59d24516e6af3ac79f283123434bfcff1d9f8a77","tid":25510,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T09:38:06.000Z","msg":"香港揸電單車真係好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}